  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And later there, they-- we have a relationship with the Jewish people, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 1936, '37, up to Warsaw Ghetto was collapse.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was not school children and not-- not student, only a relationship because my father was involved in business with the Jewish people in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's son or brother or something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was this kind relationship up to '30-- '39.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "After was different story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am Catholic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am Catholic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was a very strict Catholic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, we traditionally doing everything what's supposed to be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Catholic religion is not complicated, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You  must only go by the Ten Amendment, that's all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we go each Sunday to church and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] thank God for what happened last week and ask for better next week.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father was all the time generous and put something for the poor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we go each Sunday, each Sunday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think so that was very good, because this way is some line for young people, like we was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If-- I know other children who was not so strict-- I am not saying we was-- my father and mother was strict.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only we have some program.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sunday, we go to church.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After church, we go do something, pleasure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And was nice not only go to the church, only, after the church, my father was very big esteta.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mean was dressed nice, clean, interesting everything what was built around him, and good taste from architecture point of view.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And also, was interesting what going on around us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we go sometime to park, where are, you know, some nice tree and nice birds.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father know each bird by name.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
